+ * unlink_dev_by_name_store() - &unlink_dev_by_name device attribute store
+ *	function.
+ * @dev:	The LED device
+ * @attr:	The &unlink_dev_by_name attribute (&dev_attr_unlink_dev_by_name)
+ * @buf:	The value written to the attribute, which should be the kernel
